**Category:** gr-qc, physics.gen-ph
**Pages:** 8

**Abstract:**
We demonstrate that temporal constants encode via the golden ratio ПҶ = (1+вҲҡ5)/2 and Оі = ПҶвҒ»Ві. The Planck time t_P = ОівҒҙПҖВІ/ПҶ вүҲ 5.39Г—10вҒ»вҒҙвҒҙ s, cosmological time t_Оӣ = ПҶВі/(ОіПҖHвӮҖ), and the specious present t_present = ПҶвҒ»ВІ вүҲ 382 ms all derive from sacred formulas.

**Key Equations:**
```
t_P = ОівҒҙПҖВІ/ПҶ вүҲ 5.39Г—10вҒ»вҒҙвҒҙ s
t_present = ПҶвҒ»ВІ вүҲ 382 ms
D_t = 1 + Оі вүҲ 1.236 (temporal fractal dimension)
```

**Main Results:**
| Constant | Standard | TRINITY Formula | Value |
|----------|----------|-----------------|-------|
| Planck time | 5.39Г—10вҒ»вҒҙвҒҙ s | ОівҒҙПҖВІ/ПҶ | Matches |
